WEBVTT

00:26.141 --> 00:28.920
Candidates who passed the written exam
may now enter!

00:28.921 --> 00:31.061
(Echoes of Strength and Discipline)

00:34.571 --> 00:35.831
In the written exam,

00:35.891 --> 00:38.191
Second Young Master Song
did better than the rest.

00:38.211 --> 00:40.380
As for Mr. Mu, he succeeded
through unclear advantages.

00:40.381 --> 00:42.610
I wonder what tricks Official Mu pulled

00:42.611 --> 00:43.831
to get him through.

00:44.461 --> 00:46.290
The imperial examinations
are the only chance

00:46.291 --> 00:48.460
for commoners to rise.

00:48.461 --> 00:50.010
If such fairness is lost,

00:50.011 --> 00:51.631
won't it dishearten the people?

00:55.061 --> 00:56.330
Pay your respects!

00:56.331 --> 00:58.451
- Greetings, Your Majesty.
- Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:59.291 --> 01:00.951
Rise!

01:05.061 --> 01:07.751
The martial arts exam begins!

01:15.211 --> 01:17.441
- Impressive!
- Incredible!

01:41.061 --> 01:43.361
Having such talent on our side

01:43.861 --> 01:46.340
is like having
an unbeatable chess piece.

01:46.341 --> 01:48.471
It's helpful in achieving success.

01:52.931 --> 01:55.921
My son has some skills
in martial arts as well.

01:56.141 --> 01:58.001
How about we see

01:58.701 --> 01:59.921
how his skills measure up?

02:38.611 --> 02:40.100
Quickly, take him away.

02:40.101 --> 02:41.241
Yes, sir.

02:44.661 --> 02:46.911
The martial exams focus on restraint.

02:47.291 --> 02:49.071
Such eagerness reveals

02:49.491 --> 02:51.351
one's intentions.

03:07.051 --> 03:08.951
Who would have thought
the Song Family produced

03:09.491 --> 03:12.530
Song Yantang, who won first prize
in hunting for consecutive years

03:12.531 --> 03:15.140
and another talent who excels
in literature and martial arts.

03:15.141 --> 03:17.401
Top scores for every subject

03:17.571 --> 03:19.591
and even his discourse
in strategy is insightful.

03:19.981 --> 03:23.121
Song Han, as the top scorer,
is there anything you desire?

03:30.821 --> 03:31.961
Your Majesty,

03:32.261 --> 03:33.721
all my martial skills were taught

03:33.981 --> 03:35.871
by my elder brother.

03:36.491 --> 03:37.721
But compared to him,

03:38.221 --> 03:39.361
I still have much to learn.

03:40.101 --> 03:42.561
Today, I humbly request
an additional match

03:43.101 --> 03:45.001
to test myself against my brother.

03:45.491 --> 03:47.721
I hope Your Majesty will grant this.

03:48.941 --> 03:49.980
Your Majesty,

03:49.981 --> 03:52.100
Song Han is too audacious.

03:52.101 --> 03:53.521
The martial exam is already over.

03:53.531 --> 03:54.701
Even if he is the top scorer,

03:54.711 --> 03:58.521
he shouldn't make such
a personal request to Your Majesty.

03:59.011 --> 04:00.911
This isn't the Song Family's backyard!

04:01.611 --> 04:02.751
Your Majesty, please.

04:02.981 --> 04:05.220
Madam wants me to remind you
that your current state

04:05.221 --> 04:06.890
does not permit such exertion.

04:06.891 --> 04:07.740
That's right.

04:07.741 --> 04:09.860
You should refuse this match.

04:09.861 --> 04:11.001
I agree with him.

04:12.051 --> 04:13.351
I know my limits.

04:13.661 --> 04:14.801
So don't worry.

04:21.931 --> 04:22.900
Your Majesty,

04:22.901 --> 04:24.401
Song Han is young and impulsive.

04:24.491 --> 04:26.551
I hope Your Majesty can forgive

04:26.691 --> 04:28.321
his impertinence.

04:29.051 --> 04:30.170
No matter.

04:30.171 --> 04:31.690
Since he's the top scorer,

04:31.691 --> 04:34.911
I want to see his skills too.

04:35.251 --> 04:37.471
You shall personally test him.

04:37.691 --> 04:39.911
I shall obey, Your Majesty.

06:12.241 --> 06:16.440
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

06:16.441 --> 06:19.661
=Episode 28=

06:20.251 --> 06:22.031
Whoever captures the flag

06:22.101 --> 06:24.431
within half an hour wins!

06:28.251 --> 06:30.721
Mo, let's use the blades.

06:32.811 --> 06:33.951
Sure.

07:18.171 --> 07:19.791
If you can't beat me today,

07:20.221 --> 07:21.361
all of Official Dou's efforts

07:21.731 --> 07:23.201
will be in vain, right?

07:49.731 --> 07:52.081
I seek fame and success
through my own merits.

07:53.251 --> 07:54.881
If you want to get in my way,

07:55.251 --> 07:56.721
why not just kill me

07:57.101 --> 07:58.521
in front of His Majesty?

08:14.731 --> 08:16.031
You've taught me

08:16.221 --> 08:17.641
the adaptive technique many times.

08:17.901 --> 08:19.041
Did I

08:19.781 --> 08:21.031
finally get it right?

08:21.901 --> 08:23.321
It seems you've learned more

08:23.661 --> 08:24.911
than just blade work.

08:26.171 --> 08:28.911
To turn the tide against Yantang

08:29.491 --> 08:30.911
is rare indeed.

08:32.341 --> 08:33.410
Announce the decree.

08:33.411 --> 08:36.671
Song Han has shown
exceptional bravery and strategy,

08:36.771 --> 08:39.601
earning first place in the martial exam.

08:39.861 --> 08:41.641
I shall appoint him
as a Tengxiang Guard

08:41.891 --> 08:44.361
and grant him the Songhe sword.

08:45.011 --> 08:46.251
Your Majesty, if I may request

08:46.891 --> 08:48.361
another favor.

08:55.531 --> 08:56.671
Speak.

08:57.611 --> 09:00.401
My parents have passed away.

09:01.521 --> 09:03.001
In a time of distress and desolation,

09:03.941 --> 09:05.241
I am left entirely alone.

09:07.011 --> 09:08.151
I dare to ask

09:08.771 --> 09:11.121
for Your Majesty's grace
to grant me a marriage

09:11.461 --> 09:12.761
with the princess

09:12.771 --> 09:15.671
to live in harmony and happiness.

09:21.411 --> 09:25.161
I'll consider your marriage carefully.

09:25.731 --> 09:26.881
Thank you, Your Majesty.

09:30.891 --> 09:32.031
Hold still.

09:32.651 --> 09:33.791
It doesn't hurt.

09:35.251 --> 09:37.951
If this wound were any deeper,
it would leave a scar.

09:39.221 --> 09:40.881
It's just a minor wound.

09:41.101 --> 09:42.220
Besides,

09:42.221 --> 09:43.911
I have you as my physician.

09:43.981 --> 09:45.161
No injuries scare me.

09:46.061 --> 09:48.001
Yes, this injury is nothing major.

09:49.011 --> 09:51.281
But Song Han injured the others

09:51.611 --> 09:53.481
just to win.

09:53.531 --> 09:55.071
You must be careful with him.

09:55.531 --> 09:57.671
With Song Han's impressive performance

09:57.861 --> 10:00.191
and Lord Qing's emerging ambitions,

10:01.101 --> 10:03.481
could Song Han have pledged
his allegiance to him?

10:03.571 --> 10:05.581
Song Han has always been diligent
in his studies

10:05.591 --> 10:07.341
and skilled in archery
and horseback riding.

10:07.351 --> 10:08.881
Given the state of our family,

10:08.981 --> 10:10.730
it's understandable he wants

10:10.731 --> 10:11.770
to secure his future.

10:11.771 --> 10:14.911
But he shouldn't have aligned
with Lord Qing.

10:17.651 --> 10:19.831
(Lord Qing couldn't use Yantang.)

10:20.411 --> 10:21.881
(So he has turned to Song Han.)

10:23.731 --> 10:25.671
But you don't have to worry.

10:26.011 --> 10:28.010
Once Song Han is engaged

10:28.011 --> 10:29.351
and establishes his own residence,

10:29.371 --> 10:31.751
we can take the opportunity
to distance ourselves from him.

10:33.581 --> 10:34.721
By the way,

10:35.301 --> 10:38.241
I heard Song Han asked
His Majesty for a marriage proposal.

10:39.181 --> 10:42.031
Jingyu is the only princess.

10:42.411 --> 10:43.951
She's been spoiled since childhood

10:44.251 --> 10:45.761
and might not agree to the marriage.

10:48.601 --> 10:50.541
(Drunken Bordello)

10:51.011 --> 10:53.361
You're favoring
your son-in-law's family,

10:53.581 --> 10:56.431
allowing Song Han to rise
and compete against my son,

10:57.131 --> 10:59.031
leaving him crippled.

11:00.461 --> 11:02.410
Official Mu, that's not right to say.

11:02.411 --> 11:03.890
If I truly had that intention,

11:03.891 --> 11:05.831
why use such underhanded tactics?

11:06.581 --> 11:08.911
If your son's leg is broken,

11:09.611 --> 11:11.461
blame the Songs,

11:11.731 --> 11:13.161
not me.

11:15.101 --> 11:16.641
Everyone knows

11:17.341 --> 11:18.960
you climbed the ladder

11:18.961 --> 11:20.431
by buttering the Grand Princess

11:20.461 --> 11:21.601
and driving Wang Xingyi away.

11:21.771 --> 11:23.431
Now that the big plan isn't complete,

11:23.731 --> 11:25.431
you're already targeting me.

11:28.531 --> 11:31.831
I didn't know you love gossip.

11:32.221 --> 11:34.641
Are you looking for a reason

11:35.221 --> 11:38.001
to take my Deputy Chief position?

11:38.821 --> 11:40.481
Let's see

11:41.061 --> 11:43.311
what tricks you have up your sleeve.

11:44.341 --> 11:45.551
Fine.

11:46.101 --> 11:48.281
If that's how you feel,

11:49.251 --> 11:50.671
let's see what happens next.

11:59.131 --> 12:01.031
Han, come here.

12:01.731 --> 12:03.281
Quite grand, isn't it?

12:03.511 --> 12:05.121
What a rare sight.

12:08.411 --> 12:10.881
Congratulations.
It's truly something to celebrate.

12:12.651 --> 12:15.031
Today, let's enjoy the night with Han.

12:15.461 --> 12:17.601
Yes, make sure Han enjoys his night.

12:17.651 --> 12:19.700
I did say it during the hunt.

12:19.701 --> 12:21.460
He claimed first place in the exams,

12:21.461 --> 12:22.980
earned His Majesty's treasured sword,

12:22.981 --> 12:24.860
and is about to become
the Prince Consort.

12:24.861 --> 12:27.311
He sure has a bright future ahead.

12:27.341 --> 12:29.001
Official Song, something's happened.

12:35.121 --> 12:38.741
(I, the Princess, will not marry you.
Yours truly, Zhu Rongying)

12:42.681 --> 12:44.370
(I, the Princess, will not marry you.
Yours truly, Zhu Rongying)

12:44.371 --> 12:46.120
That Song Han is a shameless

12:46.121 --> 12:47.601
and deceitful scoundrel.

12:47.821 --> 12:49.941
You cannot let Rongying marry him.

12:50.581 --> 12:53.671
It's better than marrying her off
to Lizhen, isn't it?

12:53.731 --> 12:55.711
This isn't your concern anyway.

12:56.011 --> 12:57.431
Why are you so anxious?

12:59.461 --> 13:01.191
I'm being loyal.

13:01.821 --> 13:03.031
You? Loyal?

13:03.221 --> 13:05.311
Are you saying I'm indifferent
to Rongying?

13:06.731 --> 13:10.001
Rongying is my only daughter.

13:10.101 --> 13:12.001
Do you think I'd push her into the fire?

13:12.861 --> 13:14.890
At least Song Han
is a martial arts champion.

13:14.891 --> 13:16.031
What about you?

13:17.341 --> 13:19.311
You're the one despised by everyone,

13:19.371 --> 13:21.711
disgracing the royal family.

13:25.301 --> 13:26.521
Calm down, Your Majesty.

13:26.821 --> 13:27.730
Yu and Rongying

13:27.731 --> 13:29.130
have been close since childhood.

13:29.131 --> 13:30.881
They're always standing up
for each other.

13:31.731 --> 13:34.601
So, what do you think about this?

13:37.461 --> 13:39.401
I'm already troubled.

13:41.011 --> 13:42.831
Rongying refuses to marry,

13:43.221 --> 13:45.031
and now he adds more to my trouble.

13:45.701 --> 13:47.100
Since the founding of this dynasty,

13:47.101 --> 13:49.481
it's been tradition

13:50.491 --> 13:54.191
to grant the champion's request.

13:54.371 --> 13:55.410
Song Han

13:55.411 --> 13:56.370
has always had

13:56.371 --> 13:58.641
a rebellious streak.

13:59.011 --> 14:01.180
Besides, his background

14:01.181 --> 14:03.161
isn't worthy of Rongying.

14:03.861 --> 14:07.241
Why not grant another princess title
and betroth him to her?

14:10.731 --> 14:12.761
Grant another princess title?

14:13.371 --> 14:14.610
I've heard

14:14.611 --> 14:18.031
the Miao family of Futing
is related to Consort Dowager Miao.

14:18.061 --> 14:19.421
After the Consort Dowager's demise,

14:19.431 --> 14:21.060
the Miao Family doesn't hold
any position in court.

14:21.061 --> 14:23.131
So they fell into decline
and ventured into trading.

14:23.221 --> 14:25.870
The eldest daughter,

14:25.871 --> 14:28.220
Miao Ansu, has a good reputation

14:28.221 --> 14:30.831
and is a sworn sister
of the Duke of Ying's wife.

14:31.011 --> 14:34.551
Let's make her a princess

14:34.731 --> 14:36.340
and marry her to Song Han.

14:36.341 --> 14:39.521
This way, it's still within
the Duke of Ying's circle and closer.

14:40.221 --> 14:41.431
That's a good idea.

14:41.651 --> 14:42.791
If you say one more word...

14:54.251 --> 14:55.601
Go announce the decree.

14:55.891 --> 14:57.031
Yes, Your Majesty.

14:59.981 --> 15:03.060
Song Han is asking for too much.

15:03.061 --> 15:06.241
An illegitimate child dares to ask
for a princess's hand in marriage.

15:06.491 --> 15:08.191
He's dreaming of instant success.

15:08.611 --> 15:10.580
But that Miao girl

15:10.581 --> 15:12.340
is close to the Duke of Ying's wife.

15:12.341 --> 15:15.241
- I fear...
- Dou Zhao was a girl of humble origin.

15:15.701 --> 15:18.761
Now, she's well-connected,

15:18.981 --> 15:21.711
thanks to Miao Ansu
who is working tirelessly

15:21.981 --> 15:24.191
to make money and support her.

15:27.101 --> 15:28.241
Directress Su.

15:28.371 --> 15:29.511
Yes, Your Majesty.

15:29.861 --> 15:31.521
The princess is newly married.

15:31.581 --> 15:34.121
You will accompany her
into the residence as an attendant

15:34.611 --> 15:37.601
and keep an eye on those sisters.

15:38.491 --> 15:40.791
Yes, Your Majesty.

15:45.131 --> 15:48.881
By the grace of Heaven,
the Emperor issues this decree.

15:49.531 --> 15:51.281
Miao Ansu,

15:51.611 --> 15:55.791
a woman of virtue and wisdom,

15:55.981 --> 15:59.911
is hereby titled Princess Anyu.

16:00.651 --> 16:04.881
She is granted a golden seal,
an annual stipend of two thousand dan,

16:05.251 --> 16:09.641
and is to marry Song Han
of the Duke of Ying's household.

16:09.701 --> 16:11.191
As decreed by the Emperor.

16:11.411 --> 16:12.911
She's been made a princess.

16:13.131 --> 16:14.311
This is wonderful, Su!

16:21.061 --> 16:22.201
Xingshuang,

16:22.411 --> 16:23.711
bring a dry cloth.

16:24.011 --> 16:25.300
The snow's all over the cat.

16:25.301 --> 16:26.551
He'll start sneezing again.

16:26.861 --> 16:28.001
Yes, Young Master.

16:29.581 --> 16:30.721
Xingshuang...

16:40.651 --> 16:43.191
Greetings, Princess Anyu.

16:45.651 --> 16:46.791
Get up.

16:49.531 --> 16:51.001
I never wanted this.

16:51.821 --> 16:53.410
We should go to the palace now

16:53.411 --> 16:55.081
and beg His Majesty
to rescind the decree.

16:57.491 --> 16:59.041
- Leave us.
- Yes, Young Master.

17:01.861 --> 17:03.751
Defying an imperial decree
is a capital offense.

17:03.841 --> 17:04.981
Or

17:05.521 --> 17:07.181
do you also look down on my background

17:08.281 --> 17:09.541
and rather disobey?

17:10.361 --> 17:12.341
That's not what I mean.

17:17.841 --> 17:19.781
I've admired you for a long time.

17:22.321 --> 17:23.661
But I know

17:24.401 --> 17:26.861
the one you truly want
to marry is Princess Jingyu.

17:28.841 --> 17:30.661
For His Majesty to force me upon you,

17:30.721 --> 17:32.621
it's unfair to both of us.

17:33.681 --> 17:35.181
Do what you must as a princess.

17:35.771 --> 17:37.301
Don't sacrifice your glory for my sake.

17:40.641 --> 17:42.240
I've already written a petition

17:42.241 --> 17:44.261
stating I've fallen gravely ill.

17:44.561 --> 17:47.221
That way, the marriage can be annulled.

17:48.121 --> 17:49.261
Then

17:49.481 --> 17:51.301
how will you marry in the future?

17:59.721 --> 18:01.701
My cat is spoiled.

18:02.001 --> 18:03.501
It knows it has a home to return to.

18:03.511 --> 18:05.391
When it gets lost,
someone will always find it.

18:05.401 --> 18:06.581
So it goes out often.

18:09.481 --> 18:11.061
I'm not that lucky.

18:14.601 --> 18:15.741
The people

18:17.961 --> 18:19.141
who would come looking for me

18:20.561 --> 18:22.221
and shelter me from the storms

18:24.921 --> 18:26.261
are all gone.

18:32.401 --> 18:35.941
I'll go to His Majesty and ask him
to call off the marriage.

18:43.081 --> 18:44.221
I'm willing.

19:08.361 --> 19:09.280
(Baifu Restaurant)

19:09.281 --> 19:10.421
Su.

19:12.641 --> 19:13.840
Su, don't worry.

19:13.841 --> 19:15.720
We won't let you walk into this trap.

19:15.721 --> 19:16.491
How about this?

19:16.501 --> 19:18.080
You can hide out in the countryside
for a few days.

19:18.081 --> 19:19.800
Ms. Longevity has experience
in breaking off engagements.

19:19.801 --> 19:21.560
We'll make sure
to sabotage this marriage for you.

19:21.561 --> 19:23.241
But I've already agreed
to marry Song Han.

19:23.251 --> 19:24.341
Great. Then we'll...

19:24.601 --> 19:25.741
What!

19:26.321 --> 19:28.661
Are you out of your mind
or just being foolish?

19:29.481 --> 19:30.781
Have you met him?

19:34.361 --> 19:36.171
Song Han is good
at pretending to be weak

19:36.281 --> 19:37.511
and knows how to talk people...

19:37.541 --> 19:39.381
I'm marrying him willingly.

19:39.601 --> 19:40.920
With the honor of a royal marriage

19:40.921 --> 19:42.701
and the title of princess,

19:42.881 --> 19:44.981
this will be a huge boost
to our business.

19:45.001 --> 19:46.200
Plus, he's orphaned

19:46.201 --> 19:47.240
and needs my help.

19:47.241 --> 19:48.701
So he won't mistreat me.

19:49.001 --> 19:51.141
Also, you hold power in the household.

19:51.481 --> 19:53.320
So we'll live in harmony
as sisters-in-laws.

19:53.321 --> 19:55.661
This marriage is actually a good one.

19:55.881 --> 19:57.191
You make a convincing argument.

19:57.201 --> 19:59.200
But you're overlooking
the most important thing.

19:59.201 --> 20:00.680
You may have genuine feelings for him.

20:00.681 --> 20:02.071
But what about his feelings for you?

20:02.241 --> 20:04.421
Besides, he has questionable motives.

20:04.721 --> 20:06.821
His situation was tough before.

20:07.171 --> 20:09.021
So it's understandable
that he put on a facade.

20:11.201 --> 20:12.240
Zhao,

20:12.241 --> 20:13.960
we would often find plants
with poor roots

20:13.961 --> 20:16.181
when we used to plant rice and flowers.

20:16.201 --> 20:17.720
But with proper care,

20:17.721 --> 20:19.461
they eventually grow.

20:20.361 --> 20:23.941
Marriage is like transplanting a plant.

20:24.161 --> 20:26.661
I believe I can change him.

20:44.481 --> 20:45.400
Young Master,

20:45.401 --> 20:47.021
you've been waiting for four hours.

21:12.701 --> 21:14.381
Thank you for your guidance,
Eunuch Wang.

21:14.841 --> 21:16.021
Official Song,

21:16.841 --> 21:18.021
please be seated.

21:23.921 --> 21:26.621
This used to be
the late Duke of Ying's seat.

21:27.601 --> 21:30.381
(Secret Letter)
Now, it's yours, Second Young Master.

21:34.001 --> 21:38.181
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

21:47.041 --> 21:48.000
Anping,

21:48.001 --> 21:49.760
stop opening up the gifts.

21:49.761 --> 21:52.421
The families of nobles care about face.

21:53.601 --> 21:55.041
My sister is a princess.

21:55.061 --> 21:57.951
Even coming to his house without a formal
princess's residence is already a great honor.

21:57.961 --> 21:58.760
Keep it down.

21:58.761 --> 22:00.880
Don't let your brother-in-law hear this.

22:00.881 --> 22:02.721
You might cause trouble
for your older sister.

22:03.041 --> 22:04.160
Enough nagging.

22:04.161 --> 22:06.821
Most of these gifts
are from our business friends.

22:06.961 --> 22:08.400
He's not the firstborn
or a legitimate son.

22:08.401 --> 22:09.781
What can he say about this?

22:09.881 --> 22:11.021
Exactly.

22:11.561 --> 22:13.621
What's so special about these gifts?

22:13.841 --> 22:15.701
Gosh, stop opening them.

22:19.121 --> 22:20.200
My apologies, Son-in-law.

22:20.201 --> 22:22.061
Anping had a bit too much to drink.

22:22.121 --> 22:23.261
He's just excited.

22:23.601 --> 22:24.741
Please don't take offense.

22:28.881 --> 22:30.021
No matter.

22:31.041 --> 22:33.821
These gifts and money are meant
for Princess Anyu.

22:34.001 --> 22:37.021
Anping, are you the princess's
younger brother?

22:37.881 --> 22:38.960
Yes.

22:38.961 --> 22:40.160
Mother. Father.

22:40.161 --> 22:43.261
Since my brother-in-law has spoken,
as the only male in the family,

22:43.271 --> 22:46.421
shouldn't my sister's gift money
and betrothal gifts all go to me?

22:46.681 --> 22:47.821
Insolence!

22:50.281 --> 22:51.240
Who's this?

22:51.241 --> 22:52.381
Who are you?

22:59.881 --> 23:01.221
You dare hit me?

23:01.241 --> 23:02.501
Do you know how I am?

23:02.541 --> 23:04.440
My sister is a princess granted
by the emperor,

23:04.441 --> 23:06.021
and I'm her only younger brother!

23:07.721 --> 23:09.360
This is the Empress's jade token.

23:09.361 --> 23:11.941
Seeing this token is like seeing
the Empress herself.

23:14.281 --> 23:15.560
You, a mere commoner,

23:15.561 --> 23:18.021
dare to openly take
the Princess's gifts.

23:18.281 --> 23:20.160
Such disrespect toward the royal family.

23:20.161 --> 23:21.400
Guards, take him out

23:21.401 --> 23:22.751
and give him twenty lashes.

23:23.041 --> 23:24.341
Father! Mother!

23:24.441 --> 23:25.381
Move it!

23:25.401 --> 23:26.440
- Madam.
- Forgive us.

23:26.441 --> 23:27.600
Please, have mercy.

23:27.601 --> 23:28.920
- Forgive us, Your Majesty.
- Forgive us.

23:28.921 --> 23:30.360
It's my fault for not teaching
my son manners.

23:30.361 --> 23:31.501
Directress Su.

23:34.001 --> 23:35.421
The Princess requests your presence.

23:37.401 --> 23:39.821
Out of respect for the Princess,

23:39.881 --> 23:41.680
we will let this go.

23:41.681 --> 23:44.541
If you dare to insult
the royal dignity again,

23:44.841 --> 23:46.781
it won't be just lashes.

23:48.441 --> 23:49.901
Thank you, Your Majesty.

23:53.521 --> 23:54.611
My poor son!

23:54.621 --> 23:55.640
Anping, are you all right?

23:55.641 --> 23:58.021
Mother, my face is all swollen
from being hit.

23:58.051 --> 23:59.801
My poor son.

24:01.561 --> 24:03.861
(Noble Integrity)

24:18.121 --> 24:19.600
The auspicious time has arrived.

24:19.601 --> 24:21.541
The newlyweds shall perform their bows.

24:22.521 --> 24:25.461
First bow.

24:28.481 --> 24:30.461
Second bow.

24:32.121 --> 24:33.861
An illegitimate son marries

24:34.161 --> 24:37.040
a merchant's daughter
who turns into a princess.

24:37.041 --> 24:39.181
No wonder only
a lady official is presiding.

24:39.841 --> 24:41.581
Even the Duke and Duchess
didn't show up.

24:41.601 --> 24:42.741
That's right.

24:44.201 --> 24:45.880
The Duke
and Duchess of Ying have arrived

24:45.881 --> 24:49.381
to congratulate the martial champion
and Princess Anyu!

24:52.431 --> 24:53.581
Greetings, Your Grace.

24:53.821 --> 24:56.651
Greetings, Your Grace.

25:02.401 --> 25:03.541
Zhao,

25:03.561 --> 25:05.101
I knew you would come.

25:05.281 --> 25:06.421
Of course, I would come.

25:08.761 --> 25:10.021
Here, cover it properly.

25:12.561 --> 25:14.781
Look at all this.

25:16.281 --> 25:17.941
So much gold, silver, and jewels.

25:17.961 --> 25:20.501
- Look.
- There are all kinds of jewels.

25:21.361 --> 25:22.901
Today is the Princess's wedding.

25:23.321 --> 25:25.221
Let's all celebrate.

25:31.721 --> 25:33.501
Thank you all for coming.

25:33.561 --> 25:34.701
According to tradition,

25:34.761 --> 25:37.861
a wedding officiant should be someone
who has experienced full blessings.

25:38.281 --> 25:40.781
My parents have passed away.

25:41.041 --> 25:42.301
I once thought

25:42.521 --> 25:44.541
I would never know warmth.

25:45.161 --> 25:46.301
Fortunately,

25:47.881 --> 25:49.021
someone came

25:50.521 --> 25:52.101
into my life.

25:55.681 --> 25:56.821
Now,

25:57.241 --> 25:58.840
I treasure the beauty of a good marriage

25:58.841 --> 26:01.061
and the value of a good partner

26:01.081 --> 26:02.661
more than anyone.

26:04.361 --> 26:05.501
So,

26:07.441 --> 26:08.581
Song Han,

26:09.721 --> 26:11.461
I wish you all the same happiness.

26:12.321 --> 26:15.261
A harmonious couple
and deeply affectionate.

26:16.761 --> 26:17.901
I believe

26:18.961 --> 26:21.861
this is Song Yichun's greatest wish too.

26:26.721 --> 26:27.861
I will remember.

26:28.361 --> 26:29.360
Ceremony complete!

26:29.361 --> 26:31.200
- Good!
- Good!

26:31.201 --> 26:34.280
- Congratulations!
- Wishing them a happy life together!

26:34.281 --> 26:35.421
Congratulations!

26:37.881 --> 26:45.181
(Diecui Pavilion)

26:46.121 --> 26:47.701
Since you're here to congratulate Ansu,

26:48.121 --> 26:50.341
why didn't you attend
Ansu's wedding ceremony?

26:52.281 --> 26:54.520
A bunch of ordinary people making
so much noise.

26:54.521 --> 26:55.661
What's the point?

26:58.481 --> 26:59.701
But you all

26:59.841 --> 27:02.661
acted out a great show
of brotherly love.

27:05.601 --> 27:06.741
Why are you looking for me?

27:07.681 --> 27:10.181
I taught you acupuncture to save lives.

27:10.961 --> 27:12.461
But today I'll teach you something

27:12.961 --> 27:14.661
to save yourself.

27:14.721 --> 27:15.861
What do you mean?

27:16.161 --> 27:17.581
Leave Mantis Song.

27:25.681 --> 27:27.821
He's now a target.

27:28.121 --> 27:29.941
For your sake, and for the Dou Family,

27:30.401 --> 27:32.341
you can't follow him into danger.

27:33.641 --> 27:35.741
I just want to break free from this game

27:36.121 --> 27:37.461
to gain my freedom.

27:37.681 --> 27:39.600
Do you know who controls the pieces?

27:39.601 --> 27:40.981
Even the Emperor

27:41.401 --> 27:43.341
could be a pawn.

27:43.481 --> 27:46.141
We don't know yet who will win.

27:47.041 --> 27:48.621
Even if that day comes,

27:49.001 --> 27:50.461
I'll accept my fate.

27:52.801 --> 27:53.941
Indeed,

27:54.641 --> 27:55.880
love makes

27:55.881 --> 27:57.661
even the wisest foolish.

27:57.921 --> 27:59.341
Don't say I didn't warn you.

27:59.961 --> 28:02.181
If Mantis Song faces
a great misfortune again,

28:02.921 --> 28:04.941
the freedom you see

28:05.321 --> 28:06.981
will be in jeopardy.

28:21.061 --> 28:22.501
Congratulations, Second Young Master.

28:22.881 --> 28:24.021
Thank you.

28:26.561 --> 28:28.061
Congratulations, Second Young Master.

28:30.561 --> 28:32.781
We wish you a long and happy life.

28:33.601 --> 28:34.941
Look at him.

28:35.661 --> 28:36.901
Greetings, Second Young Master.

28:37.001 --> 28:38.680
Congratulations on your marriage

28:38.681 --> 28:40.181
and wishing you many children.

28:41.961 --> 28:44.200
He's relying on his new wife now
after his father died.

28:44.201 --> 28:45.040
Exactly.

28:45.041 --> 28:46.581
Congratulations, Second Young Master.

28:47.881 --> 28:49.021
Let's go.

28:54.761 --> 28:56.720
For an illegitimate child
to achieve this level

28:56.721 --> 28:57.960
is already incredible.

28:57.961 --> 28:59.171
What more could he want?

28:59.181 --> 29:00.920
He relied on his father
when he was alive.

29:00.921 --> 29:02.541
Then on his brother
when his father died.

29:02.641 --> 29:04.421
Now, he's relying on his new wife.

29:04.721 --> 29:06.181
I can't help but envy.

29:09.801 --> 29:12.941
(Double Happiness)

29:30.961 --> 29:32.941
Best wishes on your marriage,
Prince Consort.

29:35.081 --> 29:36.261
Thank you, Prince Consort.

29:36.711 --> 29:37.760
Thank you, Prince Consort.

29:37.761 --> 29:38.901
You can leave now.

29:48.321 --> 29:50.301
Best wishes on your marriage,
Prince Consort.

29:52.761 --> 29:53.901
Directress Su,

29:54.121 --> 29:55.421
get some rest now.

29:55.521 --> 29:56.661
Thank you, Prince Consort.

30:31.201 --> 30:32.341
Your Highness.

31:32.601 --> 31:34.360
I'm not used to people waiting on me.

31:34.361 --> 31:35.920
So I poured the nuptial wine myself.

31:35.921 --> 31:37.221
Is that improper?

31:37.341 --> 31:38.661
Your Highness, you worry too much.

31:39.321 --> 31:40.461
It's not a problem.

31:40.471 --> 31:42.141
I don't like having people
in my room too.

31:42.521 --> 31:45.501
So I've dismissed the servants.

31:46.961 --> 31:48.941
You should call me Ansu,

31:48.961 --> 31:50.181
like before.

31:50.361 --> 31:52.061
It's too formal to call me like that.

31:52.401 --> 31:53.781
A Princess is a Princess.

31:54.561 --> 31:55.701
I dare not overstep.

31:59.841 --> 32:01.221
According to tradition,

32:01.761 --> 32:03.781
shall we have our nuptial wine first?

33:07.721 --> 33:08.800
Muyu,

33:08.801 --> 33:10.640
I have a wedding gift for you.

33:10.641 --> 33:12.741
Could you turn around?

33:36.161 --> 33:37.341
Muyu!

33:51.761 --> 33:52.901
Your face...

33:57.521 --> 33:58.661
This

33:59.161 --> 34:01.181
is the handkerchief I gave you
when we first met.

34:02.241 --> 34:03.421
Did you keep it all this time?

34:16.841 --> 34:17.981
Your Highness,

34:18.481 --> 34:19.621
I'm sorry.

34:20.041 --> 34:23.861
This handkerchief symbolizes
our beginning.

34:24.241 --> 34:26.341
I planned to return it today,

34:28.041 --> 34:30.661
marking the outcome of our relationship.

34:32.321 --> 34:34.341
I'm not used to being served closely

34:36.561 --> 34:37.440
because

34:37.441 --> 34:38.821
I often can't control myself.

34:39.201 --> 34:40.240
I don't know

34:40.241 --> 34:41.741
why I've become like this.

34:42.001 --> 34:43.141
Your Highness,

34:43.721 --> 34:44.901
forgive me.

34:44.961 --> 34:46.341
I'll stay away tonight.

34:47.121 --> 34:48.341
Rest well.

35:05.961 --> 35:09.501
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

35:09.921 --> 35:11.701
Princess Anyu has arrived!

35:12.991 --> 35:14.621
Did you sleep well last night?

35:15.801 --> 35:16.941
Thank you for your concern.

35:17.041 --> 35:18.581
I feel much better.

35:21.041 --> 35:22.381
- I...
- Princess.

35:23.441 --> 35:25.000
Given your noble status,

35:25.001 --> 35:28.661
everyone should greet and serve you tea.

35:30.041 --> 35:31.181
That's right.

35:31.521 --> 35:33.021
We are all subjects

35:33.041 --> 35:34.461
and the Princess should be the head.

35:34.481 --> 35:35.921
We must respect the hierarchy.

35:36.041 --> 35:37.000
That's right.

35:37.001 --> 35:39.341
The Princess's marriage
is a favor granted by the Emperor.

35:39.441 --> 35:42.581
Why not let the Princess manage
the household

35:42.681 --> 35:44.261
to show unity?

35:45.721 --> 35:47.621
Sister-in-law is the head
of the household.

35:47.881 --> 35:49.381
So I should serve tea.

35:51.401 --> 35:52.541
Princess,

35:52.641 --> 35:54.701
this doesn't comply
with royal etiquette.

35:54.881 --> 35:58.621
The lady of the house
should serve tea to the Princess.

35:59.441 --> 36:02.101
The royal dignity cannot be compromised.

36:16.641 --> 36:18.021
The Directress is right.

36:18.201 --> 36:19.341
It was my oversight.

36:20.281 --> 36:21.421
Bring the tea here.

36:38.161 --> 36:41.821
The lady of the house should kneel
and serve tea to Princess Anyu.

36:56.201 --> 36:57.341
Zhao,

36:58.681 --> 37:00.101
- let me serve you.
- Princess,

37:00.521 --> 37:02.821
this is not following royal etiquette.

37:03.281 --> 37:04.821
If this is not appropriate,

37:05.321 --> 37:08.061
then please inform the Empress

37:08.841 --> 37:10.221
and request another princess.

37:19.321 --> 37:20.661
There's no need for that.

37:22.281 --> 37:23.781
Let's support each other

37:24.281 --> 37:27.061
in the days to come as always.

37:38.001 --> 37:40.861
(Mo's True Emotion)

37:42.921 --> 37:45.861
(Melody of Bamboo and Pines)

37:50.521 --> 37:52.640
Princess, you're of a higher status.

37:52.641 --> 37:54.541
You shouldn't be doing
such menial tasks.

37:55.321 --> 37:57.261
And that servant maid, Su Lan,

37:57.281 --> 37:59.581
how can she order you around?

37:59.721 --> 38:01.181
Where are her manners?

38:01.681 --> 38:04.040
We're friends who grew up together.

38:04.041 --> 38:05.541
There's no hierarchy between us.

38:05.761 --> 38:07.240
That was in the past.

38:07.241 --> 38:09.501
Now you're a princess.

38:10.601 --> 38:13.421
Your every word and action reflects
on the royal family.

38:18.841 --> 38:19.981
Princess.

38:21.641 --> 38:22.781
Prince Consort.

38:23.451 --> 38:25.991
This is the most popular snack
in the capital right now.

38:26.001 --> 38:27.301
I had someone lined up to buy it.

38:29.441 --> 38:30.581
Try it.

38:36.881 --> 38:38.021
How is it?

38:38.281 --> 38:39.421
Delicious.

38:53.001 --> 38:54.141
Yes, it's delicious.

38:57.961 --> 39:00.381
I'll take some to Zhao.

39:04.921 --> 39:06.061
I'll go with you.

39:16.521 --> 39:17.800
Zhao, you're slacking off again.

39:17.801 --> 39:20.181
Didn't I tell you the opera book
hasn't been found yet?

39:20.521 --> 39:22.141
Why don't you ask Ansu?

39:22.271 --> 39:24.040
She used to organize
all the books and items

39:24.041 --> 39:26.301
for the autumn festival.

39:26.521 --> 39:28.120
She knows

39:28.121 --> 39:29.461
where everything is.

39:29.481 --> 39:31.781
But now she's a princess.

39:31.841 --> 39:33.960
When I went to Xixiang Place
to assign tasks,

39:33.961 --> 39:35.501
the lady official scolded me.

39:35.511 --> 39:36.951
I wanted to reason it out with Ansu.

39:36.961 --> 39:38.261
But Song Han stopped me.

39:38.681 --> 39:40.160
Acting high and mighty.

39:40.161 --> 39:41.120
One day,

39:41.121 --> 39:43.221
they might beat us to set an example.

39:43.721 --> 39:45.680
If it weren't for Madam's care,

39:45.681 --> 39:47.121
she wouldn't be where she is today.

39:47.241 --> 39:48.981
Don't say things like that.

39:53.501 --> 39:54.861
They've been under the sun all day.

39:55.081 --> 39:56.461
But the paintings aren't dry yet.

40:00.241 --> 40:02.901
It's getting windy.
Put all these away quickly.

40:05.441 --> 40:06.581
Ansu,

40:08.241 --> 40:10.581
we'll deliver the snacks later.

40:10.681 --> 40:11.861
Let's go back first.

40:12.441 --> 40:13.741
I have a gift for you.

40:14.001 --> 40:16.151
I wanted to give it to you
during the autumn festival.

40:16.361 --> 40:17.901
But I'm not sure if you'll like it.

40:18.481 --> 40:19.621
Let's go and take a look.

40:36.881 --> 40:38.021
This is the room

40:38.401 --> 40:39.941
I prepared for you.

40:40.641 --> 40:42.901
You can grind ink, balance the ledgers,

40:43.001 --> 40:44.541
or anything you want here.

40:56.001 --> 40:59.021
Have you been sleeping here alone
these days?

40:59.841 --> 41:00.981
Yes.

41:01.641 --> 41:03.221
I was afraid I might hurt you

41:03.441 --> 41:04.581
if my illness acted up.

41:05.001 --> 41:08.021
I took you away from Yizhi Hall earlier

41:08.041 --> 41:09.541
because I didn't want you to be sad.

41:11.881 --> 41:15.421
Sometimes people just say things
in the heat of the moment.

41:16.041 --> 41:17.421
You don't need to take it to heart.

41:18.481 --> 41:20.141
They weren't wrong.

41:20.861 --> 41:22.411
When the Miao Family fell into decline,

41:22.421 --> 41:24.600
if it weren't
for Zhao treating me like a sister

41:24.601 --> 41:25.821
and guiding me,

41:28.281 --> 41:30.240
I wouldn't be any different
from the servants.

41:30.241 --> 41:31.880
Sister-in-law didn't mean any harm.

41:31.881 --> 41:33.781
She's just used to ordering you around

41:33.881 --> 41:35.341
and can't change it overnight.

41:42.001 --> 41:43.141
If there's only one person

41:44.441 --> 41:46.661
who values you

41:47.001 --> 41:48.141
in this world,

41:49.201 --> 41:50.341
it's already enough.

42:02.841 --> 42:04.400
(Yizhi Hall)

42:04.401 --> 42:06.160
Your Graces,

42:06.161 --> 42:07.741
our spies in Liaodong have reported.

42:09.641 --> 42:10.901
According to the court's decree,

42:10.961 --> 42:13.831
the grain price at the horse market
should be seven taels for every ten dan.

42:13.841 --> 42:15.821
However, Lord Qing
has secretly inflated the price

42:15.831 --> 42:17.361
to twenty taels each month.

42:17.371 --> 42:19.200
He only submits thirty percent
to the court.

42:19.201 --> 42:20.641
This has thrown Liaodong into chaos.

42:21.121 --> 42:22.800
Lord Qing is using his power

42:22.801 --> 42:24.061
to accumulate private wealth.

42:24.641 --> 42:25.720
This is a serious matter

42:25.721 --> 42:26.901
and needs careful planning.

42:27.361 --> 42:29.341
If we act rashly without a backup plan,

42:29.481 --> 42:31.581
Lord Qing might cover it up

42:31.601 --> 42:32.941
and retaliate.

42:50.121 --> 42:51.341
Sister-in-law, I'm sorry.

42:51.351 --> 42:53.880
Please don't make things difficult
for the Princess and ruin your friendship.

42:53.881 --> 42:55.640
You talk about friendship.

42:55.641 --> 42:57.370
We've been called animals,

42:57.371 --> 42:59.221
don't we deserve an explanation?

42:59.401 --> 43:00.541
If I hadn't come,

43:00.681 --> 43:02.501
were you planning
to flay Dou Zhao alive?

43:02.721 --> 43:05.360
Today, we sever our ties.

43:05.361 --> 43:06.480
If we meet again,

43:06.481 --> 43:07.821
we shall be enemies.

43:09.481 --> 43:12.991
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:13.331 --> 43:16.940
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:16.941 --> 43:22.681
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

43:23.321 --> 43:24.620
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

43:24.621 --> 43:27.700
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:27.701 --> 43:31.561
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:31.651 --> 43:35.880
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:35.881 --> 43:38.450
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

43:38.451 --> 43:39.700
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

43:39.701 --> 43:42.740
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

43:42.741 --> 43:46.920
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

43:46.921 --> 43:48.900
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

43:48.901 --> 43:52.110
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

43:52.111 --> 43:58.251
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:00.221 --> 44:07.121
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:07.581 --> 44:14.801
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:15.111 --> 44:18.321
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:18.901 --> 44:22.481
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:22.581 --> 44:28.481
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:29.101 --> 44:30.380
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:30.381 --> 44:33.360
♪Only love lasts♪

44:33.361 --> 44:37.111
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

44:37.291 --> 44:41.520
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

44:41.521 --> 44:44.100
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

44:44.101 --> 44:45.300
♪My heart feels empty♪

44:45.301 --> 44:48.230
♪But I can hear your voice♪

44:48.231 --> 44:52.510
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

44:52.511 --> 44:54.951
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

44:56.041 --> 44:56.880
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

44:56.881 --> 44:57.920
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

44:57.921 --> 44:59.261
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
